        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>Your litany rails against the sin of sloth, interfering with the target's ability to react. The target must attempt a Will save. A particularly slothful creature, such as a sloth demon, uses the outcome one degree of success worse than the result of its saving throw. The target becomes temporarily immune to all of your litanies for 1 minute.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target can't use reactions.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target can't use reactions and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target can't use reactions and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 2}.</p>"
